article.description: — Kiandre Gaddy scored 21 points as Tarleton State defeated Seattle U 69-66 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Gaddy scores 21 and Tarleton State beats Seattle U 69-66
article.linkText: Gaddy scores 21 and Tarleton State beats Seattle U 69-66
article.story: STEPHENVILLE, Texas -- — Kiandre Gaddy scored 21 points as Tarleton State defeated Seattle U 69-66 on Saturday night. Gaddy also contributed seven rebounds for the Texans (23-8, 16-4 Western Athletic Conference). Devon Barnes scored 14 points and added five rebounds. Adam Moussa finished 6 of 9 from the floor to finish with 12 points. The Redhawks (18-13, 11-9) were led by Cameron Tyson, who recorded 15 points. Brandton Chatfield added 14 points for Seattle U. Seyi Reiley had 13 points, 15 rebounds and three steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
